data.title: Edward James Ross of Parkes
data.text:
Australian Electoral Rolls...

In 1930, Edward James Ross, labourer, and wife Selina May Ross, home duties, were living off Clarinda street, Parkes.

In 1936, Edward James Ross, labourer, and wife Selina May Ross, home duties, were living in Clarinda street, Parkes. There also were [son] Charles Stuart Ross, storekeeper [and his wife] Maria Josephine Culverwell Ross, home duties.

In 1943 and 1949, Edward James Ross, labourer, and wife Selina May Ross, home duties, were living at 101 Dalton street, Parkes.

In 1954, Edward James Ross, no occupation, and wife Selina May Ross, home duties, were living at 101 Dalton street, Parkes.

-----------------------------------

Edward James Ross died aged 83 years (cemetery record).
